OL,3,CProgramme listings for SUN 17 MAY
OL,4,G2215FThe Magic of Dance with Margot
OL,5,     FFonteyn
OL,6,     GMargot Fonteyn looks at the work
OL,7,     Gof some of the greatest of the
OL,8,     Gpioneers, from the Commedia
OL,9,     Gdell'Arte in 17th-century Italy
OL,10,     Gto Martha Graham in 20th-century
OL,11,     GAmerica.
OL,12,G2315FMargot Fonteyn
OL,13,     GA tribute to Dame Margot Fonteyn,
OL,14,     Gfirst broadcast shortly after her
OL,15,     Gdeath in 1991. Featuring
OL,16,     Ginterviews with colleagues and
OL,17,     Gfriends and extracts from her
OL,18,     Gballets.
